records.name: Tuor and Ulmo
records.description: Tuor meets Ulmo and was told to send a message to Gondolin.

records.name: Saeros' death
records.description: Saeros haunted by Túrin and accidentially jumping into his death.

records.name: Túrin and Glaurung
records.description: Glaurung has taken Nargothrond and Túrin gets taunted by him.

records.name: Aragorn Arrives at the War of the Ring
records.description: Minas Tirith nearly lost Aragorn appears with the Army of the Dead and clears Minas Tirith from the evil.

records.name: Dwarfs in Bag End
records.description: Thorin reached together with other dwarfs Bag End where Bilbo was told from his plans to kill the dragon. Here the journey was born.

records.name: Erebor door opens
records.description: When the last sunlight was shining the door suddenly opens and let Thorin and company go into  the Lonely Mountain.

records.name: Bilbo finds Gollum
records.description: In the lake in the Goblin-town cave Bilbo found Gollum. Here they did the riddle game and Bilbo found the One Ring which Gollum has lost.

records.name: Fassrider!
records.description: Bilbo had the idea to leave the Elvenhalls with the help of the fasses.

records.name: Death of Boromir
records.description: When saving the hobbit from the orcs attack Boromir was hit by several arrows. In this process he died. Frodo & Sam was able to head east. Merry & Pippin were taken by the orcs.

records.name: Companion enters Lorien
records.description: The Fellowship of the Ring enters Lorien and most of all Gimli is scared.

records.name: Companion led to Caras Galadhon
records.description: The Fellowship of the Ring were taken to Caras Galadhon where Galadriel was waiting for them.

records.name: You shall not pass!
records.description: Gandalf fights the Balrog of Morgoth. In the process he together with the Balrog falls into the deep of Moria.

records.name: Companion reaches Moria
records.description: The Fellowship of the Ring reached Moria and just finds a runic gate.

records.name: Fellowship resting
records.description: The Fellowship of the Ring is the last time resting together.

records.name: The watcher in the water
records.description: The watcher attacked the companion when they tried to enter moria

records.name: Companion at Redhorn Gate
records.description: The Fellowship of the Ring trys to find a pass through Moria. The only way is to take the Redhorn Gate and the Caradhras. But actually Saruman denies them this way...

records.name: Eowyn grabs Merry
records.description: Eowyn takes Merry with her otherwhise he was not allowed to fight in the Pelennor battle.

records.name: Frodo looks into the mirror
records.description: Frodo looks into the Mirror of Galadriel and sees what will come...

records.name: Frodo fighting Shelob
records.description: Frodo was tricked by Gollum and so Shelob (Kankra) was trying to poison Frodo. Frodo was injured in that process.

records.name: The missing breakfast
records.description: Merry and Pippin realize that the journey is not like staying at home and having several meals at one day.

records.name: Arrival at Rivendell
records.description: The hobbits and Aragorn arrived at Rivendell.

records.name: 5 days after Weathertop
records.description: Aragorn and the 4 hobbits still facing the long marshes 5 days after Weathertop.

records.name: Aragorn fighting Nazgul
records.description: When the hobbits were attacked by the Nazgul Aragorn helped and attacked them. Frodo was injured during that fight.

records.name: Sam on the way to Frodo
records.description: Sam reaching the tower of Cirith Ungol where Frodo was taken to. Here in the top of the tower he saved the life of Frodo and told Frodo that he has the One Ring.

records.name: Climbing the stairs of Cirith Ungul
records.description: Frodo, Sam and Gollum need to pass the dangerous stairs of Cirith Ungol.

records.name: Frodo and Sam parting
records.description: Frodo and Sam parting from the Fellowship of the Ring and now try to find the way to Mordor on their own.

records.name: Frodo and Sam finding Gollum
records.description: After parting Frodo and Sam find Gollum or the other way around.

records.name: Taming Gollum
records.description: Frodo and Sam taming Gollum so that he is showing the way to Mordor and not flying.

records.name: Frodo & Sam on Emyn Muil
records.description: Frodo & Sam feel a bit lost on the Emyn Muil and run into circles.

records.name: Faramir shows Gollum
records.description: Faramir finds Gollum in the holy place. He showed Gollum to Frodo & Sam.

records.name: Frodo's heavy burden
records.description: Frodo feels the burden getting heavier every day.

records.name: The last steps
records.description: Frodo and Sam on their last steps before destroying the One Ring.

records.name: The One Ring destroyed
records.description: Here Gollum found his death when fighting with Frodo for the One Ring. In the process the One Ring together with Gollum were destroyed.

records.name: Frodo and Sam leaving the Shire
records.description: Frodo and Sam starting the away to Mordor. Here they mentioned that they never leaved the Shire before.

records.name: Hobbits reaching Bree
records.description: Frodo and his friends reach Bree. Gandalf told them to wait for him in the Dancing Pony.

records.name: Frodo metts a Nazgul
records.description: In the Shire Frodo was heading the first time together with his friends one of the nine that searched for the One Ring.

records.name: Frodo camping under tree
records.description: The journey together with his friends was often paused by meals.

records.name: A Song in the Trollshaws
records.description: Frodo meets the three old trolls in the Trollshaws together with his friends.

records.name: Gandalf the White
records.description: At Treebeards hill it was the first time after the fight with the Balrog that he face the companion again. From now on he is called Gandalf the White instead of Gandalf the Grey.

records.name: Gandalfs clears Theoden
records.description: Gandalf together with Legolas, Gimli and Aragorn visit King Theoden and free him from Saruman. Grima flees after that process and King Theoden is healed.

records.name: Gandalf to Minas Tirith
records.description: Gandalf together with Pippin riding to Minas Tirith.

records.name: The Battle of the Morannon
records.description: It was the last big battle in the third age. It was the same day where Frodo and Sam just in time destroyed the One Ring.

records.name: Ents release the Isen
records.description: The Ents release the Isen to flood Isengard.

records.name: Merry and Pippin in Fangorn
records.description: Merry and Pippin were able to flee from the orcs when Eomer attacked them in the night. They fleed into the Fangorn Forest where they were found by Treebeard.

records.name: Ents attack Isengard
records.description: When Treebeard saw that the orcs damaged his Fangorn Forest he was going on revange and attacked Isengard with several ents together with Merry and Pippin.

records.name: Flying to Carrock
records.description: After reaching Eagle's Eyrie the eagles brought Thorin and Company to the Carrock.

records.name: Eagles save Company
records.description: The Eagles helped out Thorin and Company in the last second.

records.name: Company in the forest
records.description: Thorin and Company trying to flee from the orcs are saved by the high trees.

records.name: Spiders attack Company
records.description: Close to the end spiders attack Thorin and Company. Bilbo was able to trick the spiders with the One Ring and help the dwarfs. Meanwhile a troup of Thranduil found the dwarfs and taken them with them as prisoners. Bilbo was not catched in that process.

records.name: Thorin and company startingbegins
records.description: Thorin and company in the Shire when Bilbo decided to come with them.

records.name: Company reached Rivendell
records.description: Thorin and company found Rivendell.

records.name: Company and the trolls
records.description: In the trollshaws Thorin and company nearly got eaten by 3 trolls. At the end Gandalf saved them in the last second and the trolls became to stone.

records.name: Thorin and the moon runes
records.description: Thoring and Gandalf got the help of Elrond to read the moon runes. Now they learned how to open the door of the Erebor.

records.name: Smaug and the Arkenstone
records.description: Thorin and Company try to find the Arkenstone in the Cave where Smaug lives.
